# 📊 Sales Performance Analysis

## Project Overview

This project presents an interactive **Sales Performance Dashboard** developed in **Microsoft Power BI** for analyzing sales performance across products, countries, and time periods.

The dashboard enables users to explore sales trends, compare product performance, and analyze regional sales using interactive visualizations and filters.

> **Note:** This dashboard was originally developed as part of a university project and is presented in Polish. All accompanying documentation, project descriptions, and analytical explanations in this repository are written in English.

---

## Objectives

The main objectives of this project are:

- Analyze sales performance over time
- Compare sales across different products
- Analyze sales by country
- Visualize geographic sales distribution
- Enable interactive filtering and drill-down analysis
- Present business insights using Power BI

---

## Dashboard Preview

### Main Dashboard

![Dashboard Overview](screenshots/dashboard-overview.png)

---

## Dashboard Features

The report includes the following visualizations:

- Sales Trend by Month
- Net Sales by Product
- Net Sales by Country
- Geographic Sales Map
- Units Sold by Country
- Country Filter (Slicer)
- Interactive Cross-filtering
- Drill-through Navigation

---

## Technologies Used

- Microsoft Power BI Desktop
- Power Query
- DAX
- Data Modeling
- Interactive Visualizations

